sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant CLI as p67 CLI
    participant CD as controld
    participant FS as File Storage
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Dev->>CLI: p67 build
    Note over CLI: Bun.build (TS) or copy (Python)<br/>Extract LangGraph topology → graph.json<br/>Create workflow.zip

    Dev->>CLI: p67 workflow deploy
    CLI->>CD: POST /api/workflow/create<br/>(multipart ZIP upload)
    CD->>FS: Unzip to localStoragePath/workflowId/
    CD->>FS: Parse manifest.yaml
    CD->>DB: INSERT Workflow record<br/>(name, version, visibility)
    CD-->>CLI: 200 { workflowId }
    Note over CLI: Save workflowId to .p67 state file
